                                  spin so common amongst ITB's)</B> </font>
                                <HR> <p></P>
                                <P><font size="-1">Subject: and you can quote 
                                  me... <BR>
                                  Date: Thu, 24 Jul 97 11:31:41 PST <BR>
                                  From: ITB&nbsp;Faust<BR>
                                  To: ;&gt;</font></P>
                                <P><font size="-1">&quot;One of the problems that 
                                  some of us older ITB's had was that the bulk 
